# Cursor Rules for Pantheon Project

## Project Context
This is a Next.js job application tracker using:
- Next.js 16 with App Router
- TypeScript
- Supabase for backend/database
- Clerk for authentication
- Tailwind CSS v4 + Shadcn UI

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all new files
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions
- Use path aliases (@/components, @/lib, etc.)
- All source code is in src/ directory

## Database
- Supabase PostgreSQL database
- Use Row Level Security (RLS) for data access
- Service role key should only be used server-side

## MCP Server
- Supabase MCP server can be configured for database assistance
- See MCP_SETUP.md for configuration instructions

